title: Tor Browser 15.0.1 Update Patches Several High-Risk Security Flaws

content.raw: The Tor Project has released a fresh update for its privacy-focused web browser. Tor Browser 15.0.1 is now available and addresses several high-risk security issues that could have compromised users’ privacy. This update is recommended for all users who want to stay secure on the internet and keep their information private.
